<db:para><db:emphasis role="bold">&lt;Unknown command&gt;<db:code>contentspage</db:code></db:emphasis>Application Windows and Dialogs</db:para>
<db:para>Dialogs can be <db:emphasis>modal</db:emphasis>, in which case the user is required to provide necessary information before work in the main window can continue, or <db:emphasis>modeless</db:emphasis>. Modeless dialogs do not prevent the user from interacting with any of the other windows in the application.</db:para>
<db:para>Qt provides a set of ready-made dialogs for file, font, color-selection and more.</db:para>
